Rainfall and streamflow for Cotter River at Gingera.

Source: R/Cotter.R
Cotter.Rd

Daily rainfall and streamflow for Cotter River at Gingera (Australian Capital Territory), from 1966-05-01 to 2003-06-07. The catchment area is 148 square kilometers.

Cotter

Format

A zoo object, of class c("zooreg", "zoo"). It is a regular time series indexed by days, in Date format.

There are three columns, P (areal rainfall, mm/day) and Q (streamflow, mm/day). E (temperature, degrees C).

Source

EcoWise?

Temperature: Copyright (c) Commonwealth of Australia.

Details

Rainfall (P)

Daily areal rainfall (mm/day).Derived from rain gauges operated by Bureau of Meteorology and EcoWise. An area-weighted average was used, with weights determined from a long-term spline-interpolated rainfall surface.

Streamflow (Q)

Daily mean streamflow (mm/day). Stream gauge ID 410730 "Cotter at Gingera". Latitude -33.592; Longitude 148.822.

Temperature (E)

Daily Maximum Temperature. Product code: IDCJAC0002 reference: 00232595.Bureau of Meteorology station number: 070014 Station name: CANBERRA AIRPORT Latitude -35.305; Longitude 149.201; Altitude 578.4 m.

Examples


data(Cotter)
summary(Cotter)

#>      Index                  P                 Q                  E
